{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"position","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/position","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath Reference</a></b>: <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT elements</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT\">EXSLT functions</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath functions</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath axes</a>\n</div>\n<p>The <code>position</code> function returns a number equal to the context position from the expression evaluation context.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">position()\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"returns","title":"Returns","isH3":true,"content":"<p>An integer equal to the context position from the expression evaluation context.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Notes","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>Note that a node's position in a context is not zero-based. The first node has a position of 1.</li>\n  <li>The context is determined by the rest of the path.\n    <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token namespace\">xsl:</span>template</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">match</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>//a[position() = 5]<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- this template matches the fifth a element\n          anywhere in the document. --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token namespace\">xsl:</span>template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n    <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token namespace\">xsl:</span>template</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">match</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>//div[@class=<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>]/bar[position() = 1]<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- this template matches the first bar element that is\n      a child of a div element with a class attribute equal to \"foo\" --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token namespace\">xsl:</span>template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n  </li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"defined","title":"Defined","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/1999/REC-xpath-19991116/#function-position\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">XPath 1.0 4.1</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_support","title":"Gecko support","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Supported.</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"The position function returns a number equal to the context position from the expression evaluation context.","popularity":0.0005,"modified":"2022-09-09T05:38:45.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"position","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"position","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"position","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"en-us/web/xpath/functions/position","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/xpath/functions/position/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/f22e42182591e38590c9add80de91a51bce3cde2","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath","title":"XPath"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions","title":"Functions"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/position","title":"position"}],"pageTitle":"position - XPath | MDN","noIndexing":false}}